oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ocoee Street
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: View looking south of Ocoee Street located downtown in Cleveland, Tennessee. Businesses in the Craigmiles Hall building include Southern Shoe Stores and Central Drugs. The sign and awning for the Bohemia theater are in the background. The courthouse was located across the street.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Drugstores; Clothing stores; Shoe stores
